<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q26_v5" title="Q26_v5" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceA</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En una imprenta, se sabe que 40 afiches grandes cuestan $28 000 y 25 afiches pequeños cuestan $17 500. El costo es proporcional a la cantidad de afiches de cada tipo.</p>
    <p>Si se mandan a imprimir x afiches grandes y x afiches pequeños, ¿cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa el costo total, en pesos?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn>
              <m:mn>40</m:mn>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn>
              <m:mn>25</m:mn>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El costo de un afiche grande es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>700</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos y el de un afiche pequeño es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>700</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos. Entonces, imprimir <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> de cada tipo cuesta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>700</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>700</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>40</m:mn>
                <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                <m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
              <m:mi>x</m:mi>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>25</m:mn>
                <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                <m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
              <m:mi>x</m:mi>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math>, esta expresión da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>25</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1&#160;120&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>437&#160;500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1&#160;557&#160;500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos. Pero imprimir 1 afiche grande y 1 pequeño cuesta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>700</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>700</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos. Por lo tanto, no representa el costo total.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn>
            <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión usa <m:math><m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn></m:math> como si fueran costos por afiche, pero esos valores corresponden a lotes de 40 y 25 afiches. Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math>, la expresión entrega <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45&#160;500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos, pero el costo real de 1 afiche grande y 1 pequeño es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>700</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>700</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos. Entonces no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn>
              <m:mi>x</m:mi>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El costo total debe aumentar proporcionalmente con <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>, pero aquí aparece <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math>, que disminuye cuando <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> aumenta. Por ejemplo, si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math>, da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45&#160;500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos; y si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8750</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>36&#160;750</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos. Eso contradice la proporcionalidad del enunciado, porque al pedir más afiches el costo no puede bajar.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Calcular el costo de un afiche grande</strong></p>
            <p>Como 40 afiches grandes cuestan $28 000 y el costo es proporcional a la cantidad, el precio de 1 afiche grande es:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn>
                  <m:mn>40</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>700</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular el costo de un afiche pequeño</strong></p>
            <p>Como 25 afiches pequeños cuestan $17 500 y el costo es proporcional a la cantidad, el precio de 1 afiche pequeño es:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn>
                  <m:mn>25</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>700</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Calcular el costo de x afiches de cada tipo</strong></p>
            <p>El costo de <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> afiches grandes es:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>700</m:mn>
                <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                <m:mi>x</m:mi>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>El costo de <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> afiches pequeños es:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>700</m:mn>
                <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                <m:mi>x</m:mi>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Sumar ambos costos</strong></p>
            <p>Entonces, el costo total es:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>700</m:mn>
                <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>700</m:mn>
                <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>28&#160;000</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>40</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>25</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                </m:mrow>
                <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                <m:mi>x</m:mi>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión correcta es la alternativa A.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>